  "Description": {
    "English": "A compact, <span class=\"name name-technology\">low-heat microchip</span>. Assembled from processed <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Chromatic Metal</span>, created from one of several specialized terrain metals.<br><br>Used in the creation of a wide range of <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个小型<span class=\"name name-technology\">低热微芯片</span>。由几种特殊地形金属中收集的加工<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>所制成。<br><br>用于创建大量<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "一个小型<span class=\"name name-technology\">低热微芯片</span>。由几种特殊地形金属中收集的加工<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>所制成。<br><br>用于创建大量<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "小巧、<span class=\"name name-technology\">低溫的微晶片</span>。須先將多種特殊地形金屬擇一精製出<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>，再將其組合而成。<br><br>能用來製作各式各樣的<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進科技</span>。"
  },
